{"about_the_game":"Nightmare Zone  is an Indie Horror Game made by two people. The dream World is like a big red room, with wooden doors on each sides: every door is a portal for a dream. Run Away from your Nightmares, explore all the areas of the dream World and find 5 doors in a row to escape. You can escape only if you can find all the doors.<br>Can you wake up? Something is looking for you and if you get caught you'll have to restart.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__21_.gif?t=1674208052\" /><br><br>Nightmare Zone is a challenge for the player: being able to complete the game can be frustrating, but that is precisely why completion can give great satisfaction! will you accept the challenge?<br>Will you be able to find in succession all 5 doors needed to wake up without getting caught by the demons that inhabit the nightmares?<br>Many others before you have tried to escape the Nightmare Zone. You'll have to be fast and brave to be among the lucky few to wake up again.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__2_.gif?t=1674208052\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1674208052","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1674208052","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1674208052","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1341710/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1674208052","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Nightmare Zone  i